er.taxAmount)}</strong></div>\n          <div class=\"grand-total\">\n            <span>TOTAL / UKUPNO</span>\n            <strong>${money(header.totalAmount)} ${text(header.currencyCode)}</strong>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"kv\"><span>Payment / Plaćanje</span><strong>${text(header.paymentMethod)} ${header.cardType ? \"- \" + text(header.cardType) : \"\"}</strong></div>\n          <div class=\"kv\"><span>Paid / Plaćeno</span><strong>${money(header.paidAmount)} ${text(header.currencyCode)}</strong></div>\n        </section>\n\n        <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n        <section class=\"tax-summary\">\n          <div class=\"section-title\">VAT summary / Rekapitulacija PDV-a</div>\n          ${taxes.map(row => `\n            <div class=\"kv\">\n              <span>${money(row.taxRate)}%</span>\n              <strong>${money(row.taxableAmount)} + ${money(row.taxAmount)}</strong>\n            </div>\n          `).join(\"\")}\n        </section>\n\n        <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n        <section class=\"fiscal\">\n          <div class=\"fiscal-title\">Fiscal verification / Fiskalna provjera</div>\n          <div>ZKI: ${text(header.zki) || \"-\"}</div>\n          <div>JIR: ${text(header.jir) || \"-\"}</div>\n          <div>Issue time / Vrijeme izdavanja:</div>\n          <div>${text(header.createdAt || header.documentDate)}</div>\n\n          <div class=\"qr-center\">\n            <img class=\"qr-code-pos\" src=\"${qrSrc(header)}\" alt=\"Fiscal QR Code\">\n            <div class=\"qr-label-pos\">Scan to verify / Skeniraj za provjeru</div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n        <section class=\"legal\">\n          Electronic invoice valid without signature and stamp.<br>\n          Elektronički račun pravovaljan bez potpisa i pečata.\n        </section>\n\n        <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n        <section class=\"thanks\">\n          Thank you / Hvala\n        </section>\n      </div>\n    `;\n  }\n\n  function update(model) {\n    renderReceipt(model || {});\n  }\n\n  update(window.appsmith?.model || {});\n\n  if (window.appsmith?.onModelChange) {\n    window.appsmith.onModelChange(update);\n  }\n</script>\n\n<style>\n  body {\n    margin: 0;\n    background: #f3f4f6;\n    color: #111827;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  .receipt-page {\n    width: 80mm;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 5mm;\n    background: white;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    line-height: 1.35;\n  }\n\n  .receipt-header {\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .company-logo {\n    max-width: 52mm;\n    max-height: 22mm;\n    object-fit: contain;\n    display: block;\n    margin: 0 auto 6px auto;\n  }\n\n  .store-name {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .store-line {\n    font-size: 10.5px;\n    color: #374151;\n  }\n\n  .divider {\n    border-top: 1px dashed #111827;\n    margin: 9px 0;\n  }\n\n  .title {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .kv,\n  .item-line,\n  .grand-total {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    gap: 8px;\n    align-items: baseline;\n  }\n\n  .kv {\n    margin: 3px 0;\n  }\n\n  .item {\n    margin-bottom: 9px;\n  }\n\n  .item-name {\n    font-weight: 800;\n  }\n\n  .item-code {\n    color: #6b7280;\n    font-size: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .muted {\n    color: #6b7280;\n    font-size: 10.5px;\n  }\n\n  .grand-total {\n    background: #111827;\n    color: white;\n    padding: 8px;\n    margin: 7px 0;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 900;\n  }\n\n  .section-title,\n  .fiscal-title {\n    font-weight: 900;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n  }\n\n  .fiscal {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    word-break: break-word;\n  }\n\n  .qr-center {\n    margin-top: 9px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .qr-code-pos {\n    width: 118px;\n    height: 118px;\n    display: inline-block;\n  }\n\n  .qr-label-pos {\n    margin-top: 4px;\n    font-size: 9px;\n    color: #6b7280;\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n\n  .legal {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    line-height: 1.35;\n  }\n\n  .print-button {\n    display: block;\n    margin: 10px auto;\n    padding: 8px 14px;\n    background: #111827;\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    cursor: pointer;\n  }\n\n  .thanks {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    font-size: 13px;\n  }\n\n  @media print {\n    body {\n      background: white;\n    }\n\n    .receipt-page {\n      width: 80mm;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 4mm;\n    }\n\n    .print-button {\n      display: none;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n",
    "js": "import React from \"https://esm.sh/react@18.2.0\";\nimport ReactDOM from \"https://esm.sh/react-dom@18.2.0\";\n\nconst Button = ({ children, className, ...props }) => (\n  <button className={className} {...props}>\n    {children}\n  </button>\n);\n\nfunction App() {\n  const [currentIndex, setCurrentIndex] = React.useState(0);\n\n  const handleNext = () => {\n    setCurrentIndex((prevIndex) => (prevIndex + 1) % appsmith.model.tips.length);\n  };\n\n  const handleReset = () => {\n    setCurrentIndex(0);\n    appsmith.triggerEvent(\"onResetClick\");\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"app\">\n      <div className=\"tip-container\">\n        <div className=\"tip-header\">\n          <h2>Custom Widget</h2>\n          <div>{currentIndex + 1} / {appsmith.model.tips.length}</div>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"content\">{appsmith.model.tips[currentIndex]}</div>\n      </div>\n      <div className=\"button-container\">\n        <Button className=\"primary\" onClick={handleNext}>Next Tip</Button>\n        <Button className=\"reset\" disabled={currentIndex === 0} onClick={handleReset}>Reset</Button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nappsmith.onReady(() => {\n/*\n\t * This handler function will get called when parent application is ready.\n\t * Initialize your component here\n\t * more info - https://docs.appsmith.com/reference/widgets/custom#onready\n\t */\n    ReactDOM.render(<App />, document.getElementById(\"root\"));\n});"
  },
